t: Amazon.com: Nate Maxson: books, biography, latest update
s: Nate Maxson is a writer and performance artist from Cleveland, Ohio. He discovered poetry as a boy the way other people find religion or drugs and hasn't looked back since. He is the author of several collections of poetry including "I Wished For A Serpent" and most recently "The Age Of Jive".
